HEADWORD: CD-R
<hw>CD-R</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[from <ets>C</ets>ompact
<ets>D</ets>isk-<ets>R</ets>ecordable.]</ety> <def>a recordable compact
disk; a compact disc on which you can write only once and thereafter is
read-only.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> compact disc recordable, CD-WO, compact disc
write-once.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

